common::Status onnxruntime::SoftmaxCPU ( const int64_t  N,
const int64_t  D,
const float *  Xdata,
float *  Ydata,
float *  scale,
const float *  sum_multiplier,
bool  logarithmic,
float *  rowmax 
)

Calculate Softmax using CPU memory.

Parameters
NNumber of rows
DNumber of elements in each row
XdataSource data
YdataOutput data
scaleStorage for scale calculation. Size must be >= N.
sum_multiplierWeights for each element. Size must be >= D.
logarithmicIf true, compute LogSoftmax. If false compute Softmax.
rowmaxStorage for calculation of maximum in each row. Size must be >= N.
